OL,6,GIdeal World has gone off air today in
OL,7,Gwhat could be the final nail in the
OL,8,Gcoffin for the teleshopping
OL,9,Gbroadcaster.
OL,11,FThe remains of the broadcaster were
OL,12,Fbought last year by investor Hamish
OL,13,FMorjaria after it was put up for sale
OL,14,Fby German investment company
OL,15,FAuerlius, who had previously asset
OL,16,Fstripped the business, selling off
OL,17,FCreate and Craft to Hochanda Global
OL,18,Fand trading its Freeview channel with
OL,19,FTJC.
