OL,6,FBut at the end of May, a company
OL,7,Flinked to Sports Direct took a share
OL,8,Fin the company. The broadcaster was
OL,9,Fput up for sale, with expressions of
OL,10,Finterest due by the end of last week.
OL,12,FSince earlier today, Ideal World is
OL,13,Foff-air or offline on its remaining
OL,14,Fbroadcast platforms. As of yet,
OL,15,Fthere's been no word regarding the
OL,16,Ffulfilment of customer orders.
