OL,6,FITV, which carried overnight
OL,7,Fteleshopping strands from Ideal World
OL,8,Fon both ITV 1 and ITV 4 discontinued
OL,9,Fthe strands at the end of last week.
OL,10,FIn a change to published schedules,
OL,11,FITV has substituted the teleshopping
OL,12,Fsegment with alternative programmes.
OL,14,FIdeal World abruptly dropped off
OL,15,FVirgin Media last month. Since then,
OL,16,Flive programming at Ideal World was
OL,17,Freplaced by recorded segments.
